ica'' with Pablo Chiereghin, Aldo Giannotti and [[Massimo Vitali]] inaugurated by Giorgio Marrapodi, Italian ambassador, Stella Rollig, general director of [[\u00d6sterreichische Galerie Belvedere]], [[Ivica Vasti\u0107]], Austrian football legend, and Marcello Farabegoli, curator and producer of the exhibition.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ambvienna.esteri.it/ambasciata_vienna/de/ambasciata/news/dall-ambasciata/2017/04/mostra-domenica-in-ambasciata-28.html|title=Ausstellung  Domenica/Sonntag  in der Italienischen Botschaft|website=www.ambvienna.esteri.it|accessdate=24 February 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://marcello-farabegoli.net/domenica.html|title=Domenica|website=marcello-farabegoli.net|accessdate=24 February 2018}}</ref>{{Primary source inline|date=April 2020}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.parnass.at/aktuelles/domenica-von-den-freiheiten-und-eigenheiten-des-sonn-taeglichen|title=Domenica \u2013 Von den Freiheiten und Eigenheiten des (Sonn-) T\u00e4glichen - PARNASS Kunstmagazin|first=|last=http://www.pion.at/|website=www.parnass.at|accessdate=24 February 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.artribune.com/arti-visive/arte-contemporanea/2017/06/mostra-domenica-chiereghin-giannotti-vitali-palais-metternich-vienna/|title=La domenica italiana in mostra a Vienna - Artribune|first=Franco|last=Veremondi|date=13 June 2017|publisher=|accessdate=24 February 2018}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://divisare.com/projects/344128-marcello-farabegoli-massimo-vitali-gianmaria-gava-domenica|title=Marcello Farabegoli, Massimo Vitali, Gianmaria Gava  \u00b7 DOMENICA|website=Divisare|accessdate=24 February 2018}}</ref>\n* 2016,  special project of the Vienna Art Week: exhibition ''The Beauty of Intellectual Property'' by Guido Kucsko curated by Marcello Farabegoli.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://2016.viennaartweek.at/en/program/site-specific-installation-kucsko-the-beauty-of-intellectual-property.html|title=Site-specific installation:  KUCSKO: The Beauty of  Intellectual